Feature: Add Employee

  Scenario: Add employee without employee ID
    Given admin user is logged in
    When admin adds employee with first name "John" and last name "Smith"
    Then employee should be added successfully
    And verify employee in database

  Scenario: Add employee with employee ID
    Given admin user is logged in
    When admin adds employee with first name "Mike" last name "Brown" and employee id "12345"
    Then employee should be added successfully
    And verify employee in database